          <title>Encounters</title>
          <text>Initial neurology consultation 12-Apr-2023 for muscle weakness evaluation. First multidisciplinary ALS clinic visit 20-Aug-2023 following diagnosis. Inpatient hospitalization 10-Jan-2024 to 13-Jan-2024 for PEG tube placement. Most recent MDC follow-up 15-Apr-2024.</text>
